The ``Say My Name`` module
==========================

Using ``say_my_name``
---------------------

First import ``say_my_name`` from the ``Say My Name`` module:

    >>> say_my_name = __import__("3-say_my_name").say_my_name

Now use it:

    >>> say_my_name("John", "Smith")
    My name is John Smith

    >>> say_my_name("Bob")
    My name is Bob 

